                "caption": "Figure 2:Overview of the proposed approach. Building on DTLR, our backbone predicts bounding boxes, class probabilities, and color vectors from text line images. These outputs, alongside learnable prototypes, are used to render characters and compose them spatially onto a predicted background. We leverage bounding box dimensions to accurately affine-render each character.",
